com.epam.finaltask.command.impl

Class CommandConstraints

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.epam.finaltask.command.impl.CommandConstraints

  • public class CommandConstraints
extends java.lang.Object
    Class, instances of that contain allowed account types and http methods to execute command with. Contains nested builder class that should be used to create CommandConstraints instances.
